<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>حذف الحساب - Delete Account | Masar Driver</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        .container {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 40px;
        }
        
        .logo {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .logo h1 {
            color: #178748;
            font-size: 32px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .logo p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .content {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .content h2 {
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        
        .content p {
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .form-group label {
            display: block;
            color: #333;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .form-group input,
        .form-group textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px;
            border: 2px solid #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: border-color 0.3s;
        }
        
        .form-group input:focus,
        .form-group textarea:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: #178748;
        }
        
        .form-group textarea {
            resize: vertical;
            min-height: 100px;
        }
        
        .btn {
            background: #178748;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            width: 100%;
            transition: background 0.3s;
        }
        
        .btn:hover {
            background: #136639;
        }
        
        .btn:disabled {
            background: #ccc;
            cursor: not-allowed;
        }
        
        .alert {
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            display: none;
        }
        
        .alert.success {
            background: #d4edda;
            color: #155724;
            border: 1px solid #c3e6cb;
        }
        
        .alert.error {
            background: #f8d7da;
            color: #721c24;
            border: 1px solid #f5c6cb;
        }
        
        .info-box {
            background: #e7f3ff;
            border-left: 4px solid #2196F3;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        
        .info-box h3 {
            color: #1976D2;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        
        .info-box ul {
            margin-right: 20px;
            color: #555;
        }
        
        .info-box li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .lang-switch {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        
        .lang-switch button {
            background: none;
            border: none;
            color: #178748;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: underline;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="logo">
            <h1>🚗 مسار - Masar Driver</h1>
            <p>حذف الحساب - Account Deletion</p>
        </div>
        
        <div id="alert" class="alert"></div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <h2>حذف الحساب - Delete Account</h2>
            
            <div class="info-box">
                <h3>⚠️ معلومات مهمة - Important Information</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>سيتم حذف جميع بياناتك بشكل نهائي - All your data will be permanently deleted</li>
                    <li>لن تتمكن من استرجاع حسابك - You won't be able to recover your account</li>
                    <li>سيتم حذف الحساب خلال 30 يوماً - Account will be deleted within 30 days</li>
                    <li>يمكنك إلغاء الطلب خلال 7 أيام - You can cancel within 7 days</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <form id="deleteForm">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="phoneNumber">رقم الهاتف - Phone Number *</label>
                    <input 
                        type="tel" 
                        id="phoneNumber" 
                        name="phoneNumber" 
                        placeholder="+222XXXXXXXX" 
                        required
                        pattern="^\+222\d{8}$"
                    >
                </div>
                
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="reason">السبب (اختياري) - Reason (Optional)</label>
                    <textarea 
                        id="reason" 
                        name="reason" 
                        placeholder="لماذا تريد حذف حسابك؟ - Why do you want to delete your account?"
                    ></textarea>
                </div>
                
                <button type="submit" class="btn" id="submitBtn">
                    طلب حذف الحساب - Request Account Deletion
                </button>
            </form>
        </div>
        
        <div class="lang-switch">
            <p style="color: #666; font-size: 14px;">
                للمساعدة، تواصل معنا - For help, contact us:<br>
                <a href="mailto:support@masarapp.mr" style="color: #178748;">support@masarapp.mr</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <script>
        document.getElementById('deleteForm').addEventListener('submit', async (e) => {
            e.preventDefault();
            
            const submitBtn = document.getElementById('submitBtn');
            const alert = document.getElementById('alert');
            const phoneNumber = document.getElementById('phoneNumber').value;
            const reason = document.getElementById('reason').value;
            
            // Disable button
            submitBtn.disabled = true;
            submitBtn.textContent = 'جاري الإرسال... - Sending...';
            
            try {
                const response = await fetch('/delete-account/request', {
                    method: 'POST',
                    headers: {
                        'Content-Type': 'application/json',
                    },
                    body: JSON.stringify({ phoneNumber, reason }),
                });
                
                const data = await response.json();
                
                if (data.success) {
                    alert.className = 'alert success';
                    alert.style.display = 'block';
                    alert.textContent = data.message;
                    document.getElementById('deleteForm').reset();
                } else {
                    alert.className = 'alert error';
                    alert.style.display = 'block';
                    alert.textContent = data.message;
                }
            } catch (error) {
                alert.className = 'alert error';
                alert.style.display = 'block';
                alert.textContent = 'حدث خطأ. يرجى المحاولة مرة أخرى - An error occurred. Please try again';
            } finally {
                submitBtn.disabled = false;
                submitBtn.textContent = 'طلب حذف الحساب - Request Account Deletion';
            }
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
